Name: Super-Skrull
Description: After the Fantastic Four stopped the Skrulls' attempted invasion of Earth, Skrull Emperor Dorrek invested vast resources into creating a superbeing of his own.
FirstComicDescription: Who exactly is the Invincible Man? What beef does he have with the Fantastic Four? And just how invincible is this new villain? A hero will fall in this shocking issue.
